title: soiree wine aerator (new & improved 2013)
description:
an introductory video to the new Soiree wine aerator.  Featuring enhanced glass design and strength, and an improved gasket to fit almost every wine bottle.

Soiree is handmade of glass and fits directly into the bottle, opening up the flavors of your wine, instantly as you pour.
